'From Squeak2.8alpha of 12 January 2000 [latest update: #2040] on 27 April 2000 at 10:48:52 am'!"Change Set:		PreserveSelectionFixDate:			27 April 2000Author:			Dan IngallsPrevents loss of editor state when moving text with active keyboard focus.  While this may sound unlikely, it is what happens when you type into a field that gets realigned as a result of the edit."!!TextMorph methodsFor: 'geometry' stamp: 'di 4/27/2000 10:37'!privateMoveBy: delta	editor == nil		ifTrue: [super privateMoveBy: delta.				paragraph ifNotNil: [paragraph moveBy: delta]]		ifFalse: ["When moving text with an active editor, save and restore all state."				super privateMoveBy: delta.				paragraph moveBy: delta.				self installEditorToReplace: editor]! !